snippet.title: Animals are so funny you just can't stop laughing - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Watch funny pets & animals and you won't be able to stop laughing! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, ducks, horses, parrots, goats... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds... So funny and cute! What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
